Name: Zzzz-Zzzz-Zzzz
About the game: When you sleep, you are dreaming. Some dreams are beautiful and vivid, the others are strange, and the rest of them are horrible... We've having them all the night, and then wake up and forget them. But what if one day your 'awakening' would be a difficult task? Could you find a way out of the dreams and wake up? Non-linear storyline Whole unique dream world to explore Various game mechanics to solve puzzles Unique mind-blow levels-dreams
